## PROJECT 1- DATA CLEANING AND DATA PREPARATION
 The objective of this project is to prepare the E-commerce raw data set transformimg the messy data into a structured format analysis.

### STEPS INVOLVED IN DATA CLEANING PROCESS
1. Handling missing values
2. Standardising date formats
3. Standardising numeric precision to 2 decimal places.
4. Trimming text data.
5. Check for duplicate records

### Tools
Excel- Power Query; The dataset contains 1200 rows of data which Excel as a tool fits for data cleaning for this project.

### Results
A cleaned data ready for analysis.
1. Date format set to mm/dd/yyyy
2. NUmeric precision of total price to 2 decimal places.
3. After trimmimg , no duplicate records found.
